</span><span class='line'> | Test::Pod             | 0        | /t/pod.t           |
</span><span class='line'> | Test::Pod::Coverage   | 0        | /t/pod-coverage.t  |
</span><span class='line'> | Types::Standard       | 0        | /lib/Anamal.pm     |
